{"tid":2362130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國多間大型銀行因應國會遭衝擊暫停政治捐款 削弱任何反拜登勢力","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T11:56:05.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"67993677b423ee883ef34f8d2702f46c0b8585c8","tid":2362130,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"美國多間大型銀行因應國會遭衝擊暫停政治捐款<br />\n<br />\n多間大型銀行和商界因應美國國會大樓遭衝擊事件，暫停所有政治捐款。投資銀行高盛表示，將可能削減對極力推翻去年大舉結果的政治領袖捐獻；摩根大通計劃暫停向民主共和兩黨捐款半年，花旗計劃現季度暫停所有政治捐款，確保不會支持任何不尊重法治的參選人。保險機構藍十字藍盾以及萬豪國際集團指，暫停向反對確認拜登勝選的議員捐款。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2374291&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=e28e2023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374291</a>"},{"pid":"b8620f669779ff66a96e4a85bd07dec21955b7ed","tid":2362130,"uid":85659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"姐係 明CUT共和<br />\n暗地裡叫中共資助民主黨LOL"},{"pid":"2e147283a939a7930a9018c22413cd0f5fe7c36a","tid":2362130,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8620f669779ff66a96e4a85bd07dec21955b7ed","tid":2362130,"uid":85659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"姐係 明CUT共和<br />\n暗地裡叫中共資助民主黨LOL"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"你係唔係無睇內文？"},{"pid":"46accacf5eab84394991a9ce8c5e68351ee2232d","tid":2362130,"uid":85659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2e147283a939a7930a9018c22413cd0f5fe7c36a","tid":2362130,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8620f669779ff66a96e4a85bd07dec21955b7ed","tid":2362130,"uid":85659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"姐係 明CUT共和<br />\n暗地裡叫中共資助民主黨LOL"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"